Tsaro mai mahimmanci a wajen Ofishin Jakadancin Amurka a Chengdu, China
Akwai tsayayyen tsaro a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka a birnin Chengdu na kasar Sin a yau Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurka suka shirya barin wurin.
Uku motsi manyan motoci da aka gani shiga cikin ginin fili, yayin da uniformed da plainclothes 'yan sanda sahu bangarorin biyu na titi, wanda aka sahu tare da karfe shingen.
Editan jaridar Global Times ta China ya yi tweeted cewa an bai wa ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu sa'o'i 72 don rufewa, ko har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200GMT) Litinin, 27 ga Yuli.
China ta tuhumi cewa wasu ma'aikata a ofishin jakadancin Chengdu suna "gudanar da ayyuka ba daidai da shaidarsu ba."
Ba tare da bayar da wani cikakken bayani ba, kakakin ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin, Wang Wenbin ya ce irin wannan aiki ya shiga cikin harkokin kasar Sin kuma ya cutar da sha'anin tsaro.
An ba da umarnin China na rufe ofishin jakadancin da ke Chengdu a yau Juma'a don ramuwar gayya ga umarnin Amurka na rufe ofishin jakadancin China da ke Houston, Texas.
Washington ta umarci China da ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare ikon mallakar fasaha na Amurka da bayanan sirri na Amurkawa."
Yayin da rufe ofishin jakadancin China a Houston ya fara aiki a ranar Juma'a, an ga wasu mutane da suka bayyana a matsayin jami'an Amurka suna watsewa zuwa gidan ta wata kofa ta baya.
Wang ya fada a ranar Asabar cewa ya sabawa yarjejeniyar kasa da kasa da na kasashen biyu kuma kasar Sin za ta mayar da martani, ba tare da bayyana yadda za a yi ba.
Rufe tit-for-tat ya kara haifar da rikici tsakanin kasashen biyu a kan al'amurran da suka shafi daga cinikayya da masana'antu leken asiri zuwa kare hakkin dan adam.
MDD ta ce dubban mayakan Pakistan da ke yaki da Pakistan a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD - Wani rahoto na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce sama da 'yan tawayen Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a Afghanistan, mafi yawa suna cikin kungiyar Taliban ta Pakistan da aka haramta da alhakin kai hari kan sojoji da fararen hula na Pakistan.
Rahoton wanda aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar, wacce aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta danganta da kawancen Afghanistan na kungiyar ISIS.
Wasu daga cikin mambobin TTP sun shiga cikin haɗin gwiwar IS, wanda ke da hedkwatarta a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta amsa ranar Lahadi ba game da buƙatun da Kamfanin Dillancin Labarai na Associated Press ya yi na yin sharhi.
Rahoton ya ce IS a Afghanistan, wanda aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, jami'an tsaron Afghanistan da sojojin Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wasu lokuta 'yan Taliban na Afghanistan sun yi ta kai hare-hare.
Kungiyar masu sa ido kan al'amurra da takunkumi ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ce ta shirya wannan rahoton, wanda ke bin diddigin kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda a duk fadin duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta cewa membobin IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabancinta ya lalace, har yanzu IS tana cikin shugabanninta Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani dan asalin Syria.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar sa ido ta samu labarin cewa wasu manyan kwamandojin ISIS guda biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun iso Afghanistan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya kwanan nan.
