Priti Patel ta bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram a tsawon lokacin da aka dauka don cire sakonnin "masu ban tsoro" da Wiley ya yi.
'Yan sanda a halin yanzu suna gudanar da bincike game da wasu maganganun wariyar launin fata da aka sanya a kan asusun kafofin watsa labarun na Grime artist.
Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida ya yi tweeted a ranar Lahadi: "A antisemitic posts daga Wiley ne m."
