Amurka "fasa-fasa" suna riƙe da baya neman magungunan coronavirus
A duniya kokarin samar da amfani anti-Covid magunguna da ake samun cikas da Amurka saboda masu bincike suna gwajin kwayoyi a "wani sabani, Willy-nilly hanya," da gwani jagorancin Birtaniya ta shirin ya yi gargadin.
Shirin sake farfadowa na Birtaniya, wanda ya shafi marasa lafiya 12,000 a asibitoci da yawa na Birtaniya, ya riga ya nuna wani sabon magani don magance cutar kuma ya nuna wasu biyu - a baya an yi tunanin cewa ba za su iya ceton rai ba - a matsayin marasa amfani.
Amma gazawar tsarin kiwon lafiya na Amurka don dacewa da wannan fitarwa yana nufin cewa sauran jiyya masu yiwuwa da za a iya share su don amfani da yawa har yanzu dole a kimanta su.
Musamman ma, convalescent plasma (jini na jini wanda ake sha daga marasa lafiya na Covid-19 kuma wanda ke dauke da garkuwar jiki wanda zai iya kare wasu daga cutar) har yanzu dole ne a gwada shi da kyau a kan babban gwajin bazuwar cutar.
Farfesa Martin Landray, daya daga cikin wadanda suka kafa shirin farfadowa da na'ura ya ce "an riga an ba dubun dubatar mutane kwayar cutar plasma a Amurka amma ba a bazuwar wadannan jiyya ba."
"Su ne kawai ba mutane convalescent jini a cikin bege shi zai yi aiki. Vast yawa da aka bai wa kuma har yanzu ba su da masaniya ko yana taimaka ko cutarwa ko ba shi da wani tasiri," ya kara da cewa Landray, wani gwani a kafa manyan sikelin-magunguna gwaji.
Amurka ta kasa yin manyan gwaje-gwaje, bazuwar kuma wannan ya ƙare har da samar da mummunan magani.
