Kansas City magajin garin maraba da gwamnatin taimako a warware kisan kai, amma damuwa game da trump ta muradi
Kansas City Magajin Quinton Lucas tambaye a ranar Lahadi Shugaba Trump muradi na aika jamiái tarayya a Amurka birane - ya ce, yayin da zai maraba da taimako a warware kashe kashe a tsakiyar yammacin birnin, yana ganin matakin zai iya zama mafi game da buoying trump ta sake zaben chances.
Lucas, a Democrat, ya ce a kan "Fox News Lahadi" na kwanan nan zanga-zanga a kan launin fata rashin daidaito da kuma 'yan sanda zalunci.
"Wannan ba haka lamarin yake a Kansas City. Mun yi shekara-kan-shekara qara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kan shi ne ainihin share wasu daga cikin unsolved kisan."
Lucas kara da cewa: "Bari mu yi kokarin samun pinpointed da niyya mayar da hankali a kan warware kisan...Ina ganin idan ka saurari 'yan kalamai... muna farin ciki da yin aiki tare da tarayya jamiái a wata iyaka ikon yinsa."
Duk da cewa yana shirye ya sa jami'an gwamnatin tarayya su yi aiki tare da dokar gida, Lucas ya ce kalaman Trump - musamman bisa la'akari da takaddama game da dabarun da jami'an tarayya ke amfani da su a Portland, Ore., sun sa da yawa daga cikin 'yan asalinsa sun damu game da kasancewar jami'an tsaro a kan titunan birnin.
"Abin da ba mu bukatar shi ne mafi man fetur a kan wuta daga tarayya jamiái yi, ina ganin, mai ban sha'awa siyasa batun," ya ce.
Trump a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa yana tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen magance tashe-tashen hankula na wasu laifuka - matakin da ke nuna fadada shigar White House cikin dokar ta-baci yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin shugaban "dokar da oda".
A "bincike" na jamiái sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da kuma sauran American birane ne wani ɓangare na Operation Legend - mai suna bayan 4-shekara LeGend Taliferro, wanda aka fatally harbe yayin barci a cikin wani Kansas City Apartment a karshen watan jiya.
Babban Lauya Bill Barr ya sanar da irin wannan yunkurin a watan Disamba ga birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - irin jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da aka tura, da kuma wasu daga cikin dabarun su, sun haifar da damuwa tsakanin 'yan majalisun jihohi da na kananan hukumomi.
Wasu 'yan majalisar dokoki daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana kan gwamnatin Trump da ke tura jami'an zuwa garuruwansu, musamman ma bayan rahotannin da suka nuna cewa jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da ba a san ko su wanene ba sun tsare masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma sun tafi da su a cikin motocin da ba a san ko su wanene ba.
Portland da aka buga tare da kusa-kullum zanga-zanga da 'yan sanda zalunci da kuma tsarin wariyar launin fata tun mutuwar George Floyd yayin da a Minneapolis 'yan sanda a tsare a kan May 25.
