AP ta caccaki sakataren yada labarai na Fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany don bayanin "siyasa" - amma manema labarai sun ci gaba da yin tambayoyin siyasa - RT News Hausa
Jaridar The Associated Press ta zargi sakataren yada labarai na Fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany da damuwa da kafofin watsa labarai ta hanyar yin mata bayani a siyasance maimakon bayani - a fili ya manta da cewa manema labarai sun zabi tambayoyin.
An labarin Asabar da AP, most US news agency, ya ce White House labarai briefings iya zama "karye hadisin," kamar yadda McEnany ya sanya su "a streamlined, full-throated talla ga shugaban kasar ta sake zaben, a wuri domin kai hare-hare a kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma wani forum gwada haske a kan bayanai" game da abin da gwamnatin da aka yi.
Na karshe wadanda assertions ne indisputable, kamar yadda wuya wani sabon bayani da aka saukar a briefings.
Abin da AP kasa ambaci shi ne, da wuya wani sabon bayani ne a zahiri nemi a briefings.
Sau da yawa manema labarai suna amfani da masu latsa White House don jawo hankali ga kansu, wani nau'in zane-zane wanda Jim Acosta na CNN ya inganta.
Sun wuce da hankula husuma kafofin watsa labarai-gudanarwa dangantaka, maimaita juna a tambayar gotcha tambayoyi da nufin kawai impugning Shugaba Donald trump.
A wasu lokuta, suna mai da kansu labarai, kamar lokacin da jaridar CBS ta Weijia Jiang ta amsa "tambayar China" ta mayar da martani daga Trump ta hanyar yin alamar da ba ta dace ba game da wariyar launin fata: "Sir, me yasa kake cewa a gare ni musamman?"
A Yuli 6 briefing miƙa wani Firayim misali da cire haɗin kan yadda briefings sun daina zama tushen m bayanai ga Amirkawa.
Trump ya tweeted cewa da safe cewa NASCAR ta talabijin ratings aka ji rauni da wani ƙarya zargin da wata kiyayya laifi a kan direba Bubba Wallace da kuma ta yanke shawarar hana nuna Confederate flag a da abubuwan da suka faru.
Tsinkaya, mafi yawan tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet a matsayin rahoto bayan rahoto ya tambayi McEnany tambayoyi tsara don sa ta ta ta ce trump goyon bayan Confederate flag.
McEnany bai bayar da amsar manema labarai so - sauti cizo cewa zai cutar da trump - amma ta sau da yawa amsa da cewa shugaban kasar ba shan matsayi a kan Confederate flag kuma cewa gist da sako shi ne cewa NASCAR magoya aka kuskure da ake nuna a matsayin nuna wariyar launin fata.
The AP ce ta busa "exaspered" a lokacin briefing.
Labarin AP ya maimaita shafi na Washington Post op-ed a farkon wannan watan ta wakilin ABC News Jonathan Karl, wanda kuma shine shugaban kungiyar Ma'aikatan Fadar White House.
Karl bayar da hujjar, "mutunta gaskiya da kuma yin amfani da White House podium for zalla siyasa dalilai ne a keta na jama'a dogara."
Amma duk da haka McEnany ta sauri mayu da combative style sanya ta a gwarzo na wasu trump magoya bayan, tun da ta ba ta farko tattaunawa a kan May 1 bayan shan kan matsayin manema sakataren a watan Afrilu.
A pressers ya kasance ba a nan fiye da shekara guda kafin ta nada.
Kamar sauran bangarorin rayuwar siyasa a Washington, dangantakar sakataren yada labarai na White House da kafofin watsa labarai ta canza sosai a zamanin Trump.
Wannan canji ya zo daga garesu da predated McEnany ta zuwa.
