Shivraj Singh Chouhan A Gwajin Gwajin Cutar Covid
Madhya Pradesh Babban Ministan kasar Shivraj Singh Chouhan, wanda a ranar Asabar ya tabbatar da cewa ya kamu da COVID-19, ya yi tweeted Lahadi da safe ya ce shi ne "lafiya" da kuma bayar da yabo ga gaba-line ma'aikata a yaki da korona.
Babban Ministan ya kuma maimaita gargadinsa daga jiya, lokacin da ya bukaci mutane da su bi ka'idoji, kamar nisantar jama'a da amfani da abin rufe fuska.
"Ina da kyau, abokaina. Keɓewar mayaƙan coronavirus, waɗanda suka sadaukar da rayukansu ba tare da son kai ba, abin yabo ne. Ina yi wa dukkan mayaƙan coronavirus na jihar wa'azi," Mr Chouhan ya tweeted daga asibitin Bhopal na Chirayu, inda aka kwantar da shi a jiya.
"Ku nisanci mita biyu, ku wanke hannuwanku akai-akai kuma ku sanya abin rufe fuska - wadannan su ne manyan makaman da muke da su don guje wa coronavirus. Ina kira ga dukkan mutane da su yi amfani da wadannan makamai don kanku da masoyanku," in ji shi.
"Dukanku ku yi hankali, ku zauna lafiya da lafiya. Wannan shi ne abin da na yi addu'a ga Allah," Mr Chouhan ya kara da cewa.
A ranar Asabar Mr Chouhan ya yi tweeted cewa ya kamu da cutar duk da kokarin da ya yi don kauce wa kamuwa da cutar kuma ya yi gargadin cewa "kawai dan rashin kula yana kiran coronavirus."
Da yake magana da safiyar yau Mr Chouhan ya ce duk da barazanar kamuwa da cutar babu "babu bukatar jin tsoro" kuma ya bukaci wadanda ke nuna alamun cutar da su yi gwaji da kansu.
"Idan kun kamu da cutar, babu bukatar ku ji tsoro. Kada ku ɓoye alamun cutar amma ku gaya wa likitoci nan da nan, don haka za a iya fara magani. Magani na lokaci zai sa ku lafiya," in ji shi.
Madhya Pradesh tana da kusan 27,000 masu kamuwa da COVID-19, wanda sama da 7,600 ke aiki kuma 799 sune mutuwar da ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar.
Indiya ta samu karuwar masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin makonnin da suka gabata, inda aka gano sama da sabbin mutane 45,000 a kowace rana tun daga 23 ga Yuli.
Adadin wadanda aka tabbatar sun kamu da cutar coronavirus yana gabatowa da sauri 14 lakh; daga cikin wadannan fiye da 4.67 lakh sune masu aiki kuma sama da 32,000 sune mutuwa da ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar.
Karuwar lamura, daidai da tsagaita shakatawa na ka'idojin kulle a yankunan da ba a kiyayewa ba na kasar, ya fitar da Indiya zuwa na uku a jerin al'ummomin da abin ya fi shafa.
Kawai Amurka (41.78 lakh lokuta) da Brazil (23.94 lakh lokuta) ne mafi muni kashe.
Tunisia ministan cikin gida mai suna sabon PM, ya kafa gwamnati a cikin wata guda
An nada Hichem Mechichi ministan harkokin cikin gida na Tunisia don ya kafa gwamnati ta gaba, in ji ofishin shugaban kasar, a yayin rikicin siyasa tsakanin manyan jam'iyyu a Arewacin Afirka.
Lauyan mai shekaru 46 ya yi nasara a kan Elyes Fakhfakh, wanda ya yi murabus a matsayin firayim minista a farkon wannan watan.
Amma Mechichi bai kasance daya daga cikin sunayen da jam'iyyun siyasa suka gabatar wa Shugaba Kais Saied ba.
A wata sanarwa bayan sanarwar da ya fitar ranar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce "zai yi aiki don kafa gwamnatin da za ta dace da tsammanin duk 'yan Tunisiya."
Tunisia da aka yaba a matsayin rare nasara labarin for dimokuradiyya miƙa mulki bayan Arab Spring yankin tashin hankali tartsatsi ta haifar da ta 2011 juyin juya halin.
Amma shugabanninta sun yi gwagwarmaya don biyan bukatun al'ummar Tunisiya kuma tattalin arzikin da ya riga ya lalace sakamakon rufe iyakokin kasar saboda annobar COVID-19.
Cutar ta kashe kusan mutane 50 kuma ta kamu da cutar fiye da 1,400 a Tunisia.
Kazalika, kasancewa ministan cikin gida a cikin gwamnati mai barin gado, Mechichi ya kasance mai ba da shawara ga Shugaba Saied, da ke tafiyar da al'amura na shari'a.
Ya kasance a baya shugaban ma'aikata a ma'aikatar sufuri da kuma aiki a ma'aikatar harkokin jama'a.
A halin yanzu dai yana da wata guda da zai kafa gwamnati, wacce a wannan lokacin za ta fuskanci kuri'ar amincewa ta majalisa sannan kuma za ta bukaci gagarumin rinjaye da za ta yi nasara.
Kasawa cewa, majalisar dokoki za a rushe da kuma sabon zaben da za a gudanar a cikin watanni uku.
A zaben karshe da aka gudanar a watan Oktoba, jam'iyyar Ennahdha ta hau kan gaba amma ta fadi kasa da mafi yawa kuma daga bisani ta amince ta shiga gwamnatin hadin gwiwa.
Fakhfakh ta yi murabus a ranar 15 ga watan Yuli, bayan kasa da watanni biyar a kan karagar mulki, barazanar sabon siyasa deadlock a cikin al'umma, kamar yadda fama da tattalin arziki fallout na annobar.
The murabusation zurfafa siyasa muhawara tare da Ennahdha kan zargin da Fakhfakh na rikice-rikice na ban sha'awa.
Dangantaka tsakanin shugaban mai barin gado mai shekaru 47 da Ennahdha ta yi tsami tun daga zaben majalisar dokoki na watan Oktoba.
Fakhfakh ya sauka a wannan rana da jam'iyyar ta shigar da kara ba tare da amincewa da shi ba.
Ennahdha ya farko zabi mai zaman kanta ga firaministan kasar, amma ya kasa lashe goyon bayan majalisar dokoki, manyan shugaban kasar don sunan tsohon ministan kudi Fakhfakh ga post.
A karshe dai Ennahdha ya amince da shiga cikin gwamnatin hadin gwuiwa.
