Duk da haka, Mr Callaghan ce online masu ba da bashi sun disadvantaged idan aka kwatanta da babban bankuna domin ba su da damar yin amfani da wannan ƙananan saka farashi kudade da kuma yi gargadin a sakamakon da SME tabbacin makirci da aka ba samun gogayya.
"Ina ganin ya yiwuwa rasa alamar inda duk mutanen da suka kira mu, kira a cikin fata za su iya samun sosai cheap kudade maimakon gwamnati goyon baya 50 cent na rance," in ji shi.
"Saboda haka suna kira kuma suna baƙin ciki sosai saboda an fitar da tsammanin a can cewa akwai farashi mai rangwame kuma muna duban farashinmu na kudade wanda bai canza ba kwata-kwata."
Mr Callaghan ya kara da cewa idan fintechs sun sami damar samun dama mai rahusa kudade da kuma wuce da cewa a kan kananan harkokin kasuwanci makirci zai zama "babu mai kwakwalwa."
"Yana da wani bit na a Kama 22 manyan bankuna sun samu damar yin amfani da ƙananan kudin kudade amma sun fi hadarin ƙi don haka ba su da zahiri fita don bayar da rance a cikin wannan hanya, ba za su iya samun damar yin amfani da bayanai da kuma ba za su iya samun dadi sai dai idan kana da dukiya,"In ji shi. "Har za mu iya samun damar cewa mai rahusa kudade ina ganin akwai wani labari fita a kasuwa a kan yadda m makirci."
Melbourne-tushen Moula ne ma halartar makirci da kuma shugaban zartarwa Aris Allegos ce amfanin da 50 cent garanti, fakaice a cikin gwamnatin makirci, ya kamata a wuce zuwa kananan harkokin kasuwanci amma daban-daban masu ba da bashi da aka handling wannan a hanyoyi daban-daban.
"Zan iya fahimtar akwai wasu da ba sa wucewa ta wannan tsarin kudin," in ji shi.
"Wannan zai iya zama wani aiki na yadda su kudade da aka tsara da kuma shi zai zama wani aiki ma na abin da Categories suna lamuntawa a cikin da kuma yadda za su tantance hadarin cikin wadanda Categories."
Mr Allegos ba zai bayar da cikakken bayani game da yawan rance Moula ya bayar a karkashin makirci, amma ya ce revamped makirci ne "a core fitarwa na abin da ake bukata don canja" don bayar da mafi sassauci ga masu ba da bashi da kuma borrowers.
Duk da haka, ya ce babban abin da ya fi damunsa shi ne "tattalin arziki mai sauri guda biyu" da ke aiki da kuma tasirin da hakan zai yi ga kananan kamfanoni.
"Babban batun Moula ya fuskanci da kuma masu ba da bashi game da kananan harkokin kasuwanci ne cewa karin magana da dutse da kuma yadda za a gudanar a cikin wannan dutse," in ji shi.
"Kullum magana game da bukatar ba mu koma pre-COVID matakan ko da yake ci yana girma."
ASX-jera online mai ba da bashi Prospa kuma ba zai daki-daki, adadin rance da ya bayar a karkashin makirci kamar yadda ya ce da bayanai da aka harkokin kasuwanci m amma shugaban zartarwa Greg Moshal ce goverment ta tsawo daga cikin makirci ya maraba.
"Mun goyi bayan wani kayan haɓɓaka zuwa makirci cewa zai taimaka kananan harkokin kasuwanci don samun damar da fadi da kewayon kudade kayayyakin da cewa hadu da bukatun, ciki har da m tsabar kudi kwarara kayayyakin kan guntu sharuddan," ya ce.
